Title: Loss of Causality in Discretized Light-Cone Quantisation
Authors: T. Heinzl, H. Kr\"oger and N. Scheu
Comments: Text (REVTEX file) + 4 figures (4 epsf files + 4 ps files)
\\
  We demonstrate that front form quantisation with periodicity in a compact
light-like direction (discretized light-cone quantisation) violates
microcausality.
